{
  "page": "Rickard Ryswell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\"><img alt=\"House Ryswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/50px-House_Ryswell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/75px-House_Ryswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/100px-House_Ryswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Rickard Ryswell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\"><img alt=\"House Ryswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/50px-House_Ryswell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/75px-House_Ryswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4d/House_Ryswell.svg/100px-House_Ryswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Ryswell_Brothers_by_Amuelia.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Ryswell Brothers by Amuelia.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/20/Ryswell_Brothers_by_Amuelia.jpg/300px-Ryswell_Brothers_by_Amuelia.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/20/Ryswell_Brothers_by_Amuelia.jpg/450px-Ryswell_Brothers_by_Amuelia.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/20/Ryswell_Brothers_by_Amuelia.jpg/600px-Ryswell_Brothers_by_Amuelia.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Rickard, Roose, and Roger Ryswell by Amuelia</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\">House Ryswell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Ryswell\" title=\"Rodrik Ryswell\">Rodrik Ryswell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Rickard Ryswell</b> is a son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Ryswell\" title=\"Rodrik Ryswell\">Rodrik Ryswell</a> and a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\">House Ryswell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rickard_Ryswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Rickard's look resembles that of his brother <a href=\"/index.php/Roger_Ryswell\" title=\"Roger Ryswell\">Roger</a>, to the point <a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> struggles to tell them apart.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Rickard and his brothers Roger and <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Ryswell\" title=\"Roose Ryswell\">Roose</a> are said to be quarrelsome. They each take a horsehead of a different color for their sigil, the jape being that the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\">Ryswells</a> cannot even agree upon the color of their arms.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rickard_Ryswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rickard_Ryswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a> sees a Ryswell lead a <a href=\"/index.php/Column\" title=\"Column\">column</a> of riders to the camp of <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Moat_Cailin\" title=\"Siege of Moat Cailin\">siege of Moat Cailin</a>, but is unable to tell the difference between Rickard and his brother <a href=\"/index.php/Roger_Ryswell\" title=\"Roger Ryswell\">Roger</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Along with the rest of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ryswell\" title=\"House Ryswell\">House Ryswell</a>, Rickard attends <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Ramsay_Bolton_and_Arya_Stark\" title=\"Wedding of Ramsay Bolton and Arya Stark\">the wedding</a> of Ramsay to \"<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a>\"—actually <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Jeyne Poole</a>—in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. Theon spots Rickard nuzzling at the neck of one of <a href=\"/index.php/Abel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Abel\">Abel</a>'s washerwomen—supposedly <a href=\"/index.php/Frenya\" title=\"Frenya\">Frenya</a>—near the <a href=\"/index.php/Burned_Tower\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Burned Tower\">Burned Tower</a> of Winterfell (however, as mentioned before, it is possible Theon mistakes Roger for Rickard).<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> After a foolish <a href=\"/index.php/Freerider\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Freerider\">freerider</a> is thrown from the <a href=\"/index.php/Battlements_Gate\" title=\"Battlements Gate\">Battlements Gate</a>, Rickard laughs at his fate.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rickard_Ryswell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span